{"tid":169051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位裝修JJ 地盤JJ, 所有識水泥JJ，有事相求！","createTime":"2017-03-24T03:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T06:21:33.000Z","uid":75105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef24d9ce4f151f2160af3cb32bf9bd8551cdad4b","tid":169051,"uid":75105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"我近排因爲有啲事，需要用到水泥，但之前完全冇接觸過，所以有好多on9問題想問。<br />\n<br />\n水泥一般有分幾多種同有咩唔同既用途？ 以我所知都係黑英同白英<br />\n<br />\n英泥一般同水既比例係幾多到？ 多左同少左會有咩問題？ 唔同水泥既水既比例又係點？<br />\n<br />\n英泥加水之後需唔需要搞拌？如果要的話，大約搞到咩程度先可以上？<br />\n<br />\n之前網上都有睇過，有時會加啲沙上去。點解要加？ 個啲係咪沙灘個啲沙黎？ 除左沙之外 仲會加乜野？ 同加沙既分別係邊？ <br />\n<br />\n請求各位詳細解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df0e982e614d802b3d4a9ca5d4878a5958f44c0","tid":169051,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"專業既野留返比專業既人搞啦<br />\n<br />\n你都係乖乖地旁水"},{"pid":"1cfe700f12d69ba2676b65f382d355bd5a0e323d","tid":169051,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"樓主想用水泥做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044dd467644050a03cc3dcfe1cfb698c3cc9f37c","tid":169051,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主想用水泥做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n封....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr